    rawplus_ae

    rawplus_ae.Rd

    Adverse Events (ae) data in rawplus format.

    Usage

    rawplus_ae

    Format

    a data frame with 4854 rows and 127 columns.

    studyid

    string Study Identifier

    siteid

    string Site Identifier

    invid

    string Investigator ID

    scrnid

    string Screen Identifier

    subjid

    string Subject Identifier

    subjectid

    string System Subject Identifier

    datapagename

    string eCRF Page Name

    datapageid

    string Internal ID for Data Page

    foldername

    string Folder Name

    instancename

    string Instance Name

    recordid

    string Record Identifier

    record_dt

    string Record Date

    recordposition

    float Record Position

    mincreated_dts

    string Earliest Data Creation Date/Time

    maxupdated_dts

    string Latest Data Update Date/Time

    aeterm

    string Reported Term for the Adverse Event

    aeser

    string Serious Event

    aest_dt

    string Start Date/Time for Adverse Event

    aeen_dt

    string End Date/Time for Adverse Event

    aeongo

    string AE Ongoing

    aerel

    string Pass through label from RAW

    aerel1

    string Pass through label from RAW

    aerel2

    string Pass through label from RAW

    string Pass through label from RAW

    string Pass through label from RAW

    aeacn2

    string Pass through label from RAW

    caseno

    string Case ID

    string Result in Death

    string Is Life Threatening

    string If Hospitalized, Date Discharged

    aesdisab

    string Persis of Signif Disability/Incapacity

    aescong

    string Congenital Anomaly or Birth Defect

    aesmie

    string Other Medically Important Serious Event

    aediseas

    string Study Disease-related

    aeprecon

    string Pre-existing Condition

    aeinter

    string Intercurrent Illness

    aecm

    string Concomitant Medications

    string Specify Concomitant Medications

    aeoth

    string Other Causality

    aeothsp

    string Specify Other Causality

    aeout

    string Outcome of Advese Event
